  "texts": [
    "In CycleGAN, the generator G AB and discriminator D B work for a single pair using an adversarial loss L GAN G AB, D B as defined in Eq. 5.",
    "However, the adversarial loss for reverse mapping pair G BA and D A is denoted as L GAN G BA, D A.",
    "So, a cycle-consistency loss is proposed to minimize the reconstruction error from image translation of one domain to another domain.",
    "The cycleconsistency loss is defined in Eq. 6.",
    "The final loss of the CycleGAN is formulated as Eq. 7."
  ],
